name: Borscht
instructions: Stew beets, beef chunks, onions, carrots, and whatever else you'd like in a pot for 70 minutes.

name: Chicken Salad
instructions: Chop up cooked chicken and whatever salad bits you'd like, and toss them in a bowl.

name: Waffles
instructions: Press pancake or waffle batter in a waffle iron until done, then top with whatever you please.

name: Osso Buco
instructions: Braise veal with vegetables, white wine, and broth.
